## 📋 EXECUTION OPTIONS

### Option 1: Direct Copy-Paste (RECOMMENDED)

1. **On Windows machine (igor-gaming):**
   - Open PowerShell as Administrator
   - Navigate to Desktop: `cd $env:USERPROFILE\Desktop`
   - Create script file:
     ```powershell
     notepad deep_clean_scan.ps1
     ```
   - Copy entire contents from: [/home/gonya/01_Projects/PRJ-004_AI_Agents/deep_clean_scan.ps1](file:///home/gonya/01_Projects/PRJ-004_AI_Agents/deep_clean_scan.ps1)
