## 🚀 QUICK START COMMAND

**Copy this entire block and paste into PowerShell (as Admin):**

```powershell
# Quick deployment
cd $env:USERPROFILE\Desktop
Invoke-WebRequest -Uri "http://100.88.65.71:8000/deep_clean_scan.ps1" -OutFile "deep_clean_scan.ps1" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue
if (Test-Path "deep_clean_scan.ps1") {
    Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope Process -ExecutionPolicy Bypass
    .\deep_clean_scan.ps1
} else {
    Write-Host "❌ Could not download script. Use manual copy-paste method." -ForegroundColor Red
}
```

