## 📞 SUPPORT

If you encounter errors:
1. Ensure PowerShell is running as Administrator
2. Check execution policy: `Get-ExecutionPolicy`
3. Temporarily bypass: `Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope Process -ExecutionPolicy Bypass`
4. Report errors to Chief Storage Officer

